Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正细雅宋_GBK\fs45\bord0.5\blur7\3c&HACB0B6&\fade(0,100)\frz3.013\pos(357,618)}不改写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正细雅宋_GBK\fs55\bord0.5\blur7\3c&HACB0B6&\fade(100,300)\frz359.9\pos(636,462)}改写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给我打下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,距离目标还有500
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,400
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机被…击落了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪?  超人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是那个内奸?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,篝  郊游该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  篝  就这样保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,星球会…消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这还说不准
